name: Rhapsody in the Rain
comments: The initial release of this work was banned on many radio stations in the US as in the uncensored version the lyrics contained texts like: "We were makin' out in the rain" and "In this car, our love went much too far". The original lyrics were changed from: "We were makin' out in the rain" to "We fell in love in the rain" and "In this car, we went too far" to "Our love came like a falling star."
